roducibility of\nthe regime map for liquid-liquid systems is assessed. The present lattice\nBoltzmann simulations well reproduce the characteristics of predicted regimes,\nincluding varicose breakup, sinuous breakup, and atomization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 May 2017 01:40:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Jun 2017 15:46:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
