 network, for example reflecting itself in a persistent hierarchy\nbetween the four triadic energies, and in the consistency of the extracted\nparameters from comparing the model Hamiltonian to the data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 May 2017 14:57:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Aug 2017 12:33:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 24 Aug 2017 15:39:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-30"}
